@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rvmgto(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (((v2 + 0.75 + v0 + 0.99) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.39)) - (tmp - (v0 + 0.77 + v0 + 0.26)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.53)))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.45 - tmp + 0.89)) / wp.exp((v2 + 0.67 * tmp + 0.56)))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
